{"type": "article", "id": 9827, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-05-21T08:12:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1108, "name": "相机"}, {"id": 3149, "name": "灯具"}, {"id": 448, "name": "家具"}, {"id": 10436, "name": "自动灌溉"}, {"id": 3603, "name": "包"}, {"id": 413, "name": "耳机"}, {"id": 10437, "name": "Beautiful People"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 8752, "name": "Lexon"}, {"id": 8874, "name": "Fujifilm"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135810Uhnb62ul4fAz7kTO.png", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tTableau by Pikaplant\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t来自荷兰的设计工作室 Pikaplant 最近推出了一个叫做 “Tableau” 的自动灌溉系统，这个系统包括三个陶瓷花盆，一个连接到蓄水盆的金属基底，模仿植物的自然循环，能够自动给植物浇水。设计简单干净，几乎适合摆放在家里任何位置。目前售价 125 欧元，正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/pikaplant/tableau-automatic-house-plant-watering-tray\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210614b95g8PSDFacwhIKW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210614hxcWiEkC0tmFV8d5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210615mREDtQWpryMkCn0v.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210615i46VSetP5aZc0Nfz.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052106171FOBDPASyQ4GXfWl.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210618noPqFwCGZVU1TDNz.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tX-T10 by Fujifilm\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tFujifilm 最近为 X 系列新添无反相机 X-T10。比起 X-T1 来看，X-T10 更加小巧精致，重量仅为 381g，新增了弹出式闪光灯设计，采用银黑配色，整体风格复古优雅。材料上使用铝镁合金，机顶上设有三个铝合金转盘，使用者可以通过简单的拨杆快速切换成全自动拍摄模式。这个系列将在今年 6 月发售。<a href=\"http://www.fujifilm.com/products/digital_cameras/x/fujifilm_x_t10/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210619aZevgwNQphi9MJq2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66538462\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210619Y8HvBdJmCAGxMznX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210619oTUfPc5Y1Jjq04Hu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53691275\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210620kxBLfopEJOYVbRiQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53691275\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tCreative Toolkit by Master &amp; Dynamic X Zero Halliburton \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t耳机品牌 Master &amp; Dynamic 日前与行李箱品牌 Zero Halliburton 联合推出了一个名为 “Creative Toolkit” 的行李箱耳机系列。这个铝手提箱里面设置了一个 MH40 或 MH30 头戴式耳机，一个耳机支架，一个话筒线，一个帆布耳机包和一个皮制线缆盒。产品定价 750 美元，<a href=\"http://www.masterdynamic.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210621YxVP3updTDaLrkNn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210621IwTuemMRvKAYcd1G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210621j5x1MYGOcbKmBNvQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210622wF301DIMpRn7eO6W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tYari by Lexon\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t这是 Lexon 推出的一款极简台灯，灯杆采用铝合金管，而灯座则选用的是 ABS 橡胶，材质十分轻盈。灯杆可以旋转 120 度，方便使用者调整角度，方便自己的使用，以及“拗造型”。同时，这款台灯配备有一个 USB 接口，可以给其他小型电器如手机等电子设备充电。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210622yETe7GLJcQr8gMOw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57701711\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210623DB5HKXmC6MdSUiRq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210623uBIlL1xFR7HYQfjy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210624bfOSP6JX9eljVDLv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210624GOuFs5bcnPNH3AE0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210625LwESVqe64zd7Tnfu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tSuntan by Nendo\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t天然皮革会随着时间的流逝转变颜色和感觉，形成个人独一无二的印记。Nendo 从这个角度出发，为皮革制品涂上了无色的 SPF 50 防晒油，在使用中随着时间的推移，皮具会显示出各种不同的图案，而随着更多时间的暴露，标记又会随着整体的剥落全部消失。“Suntan 图案”有条纹，方格，圆点，信封式四种设计，而五款产品分别是文件夹、书皮、名片夹、收纳盒和一款凳子。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210625Q7e2ZvfBi30o6TLX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70687023\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060521062685twO9ovcRKdB30D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210626l1WVbuG8riJvN3Q6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210627efnoUlmgaIWGMpQT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210627Qf3iTJ1b5X2NZVlK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210628uTyMDNY5hezUZqCj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210629lXHrpQ2wTe3bJzxd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tNew Collection by Beautiful People \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t机车包不要光盯着巴黎世家了，日本品牌 Beautiful People 最近推出了一个以 Biker Jacket 为灵感的皮具系列，包括单肩包，皮夹，名片夹等等，黑色的皮具和金色的金属配件搭配在一起，营造出浓浓的街头帅气感。材质上选用的是柔软的小羊皮，即使磨损，也会散发出用旧后的特别气质。不过目前这个系列只在 Beautiful People 日本青山店和大阪店出售，感兴趣的得需要代购了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210629ED3c4QftmVI5daBs.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;white-space:normal;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210630eOaAZg1t2X9xYuC8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210630WxJjvNGBzyY75bDC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210630DKEoR7Szx1Ygy3kq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210631d58olsN4FITjHuD0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210631NtRMf3HunzqObKJQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210632oGD5WNagx4tIunrd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}